dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, depths shown by soundings and isolines. Includes "Objects of special interest in natural History. Conchology. Botany." "The figures have reference to the conchology, the letters to the botany." Originally issued folded in covers 17 x 11 cm.
dct_publisher_sm: [St. Peter, Guernsey?] : Published by Thomas Grigg, printer & bookseller, 1880.
